Terrorsaur:





Terrorsaur squinted at the conversation. The wolf KitKat just 
nominated herself new leader? And now she thinks she can make her own 
plans? He shook his head. "This is pathetic!" He left KitKat's 
quarters and walked to the main section of the cave. He walked out of 
the mouth and stood by the auto-guns, looking up at the sky.
